OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F346A1782778699
OL,3,CFundraiser passes #20000 for fired
OL,4,CMorrisons manager who confronted
OL,5,Cshoplifter
OL,7,FA fundraiser for a man who was fired
OL,8,Ffrom his job as a Morrisons store
OL,9,Fmanager after challenging a serial
OL,10,Fshoplifter has passed #20,000.
OL,12,F46-year-old Sean Egan was a manager at
OL,13,Fthe Aldridge store near Walsall for 29
OL,14,Fyears, when he was dismissed following
OL,15,Fthe incident in December.
OL,17,FThe fundraiser was set up by members
OL,18,Fof the community to contribute towards
OL,19,Fthe legal costs for his tribunal.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,347,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F346A1782778699
OL,3,CFundraiser passes #20000 for fired
OL,4,CMorrisons manager who confronted
OL,5,Cshoplifter
OL,7,FOrganisers said: "After decades of
OL,8,Floyal service, (Sean) is taking his
OL,9,Fcase to an employment tribunal to
OL,10,Fchallenge what he believes is an
OL,11,Funfair and disproportionate outcome.
OL,13,F"This isn't just about one moment,
OL,14,Fit's about fairness, loyalty, and
OL,15,Fstanding up for what's right.
OL,17,F"While fighting this, Sean is also
OL,18,Funder real financial pressure. Like
OL,19,Fmany of us, he has a mortgage to pay
OL,20,Fand bills that don't stop even when
OL,21,Flife takes an unexpected turn.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,347,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F346A1782778699
OL,3,CFundraiser passes #20000 for fired
OL,4,CMorrisons manager who confronted
OL,5,Cshoplifter
OL,7,F"That's where we come in as a
OL,8,Fcommunity."
OL,10,FIn December 2025, a repeat shoplifter
OL,11,Fbecame abusive and spat in Mr Egan's
OL,12,Fface during a confrontation over
OL,13,Fstolen goods. Mr Egan then escorted
OL,14,Fthe shoplifter from the store.
OL,16,FMorrisons dismissed Mr Egan on the
OL,17,Fgrounds of not following its "deter-
OL,18,Fand-not-detain" policy.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,347,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F346A1782778699
OL,3,CFundraiser passes #20000 for fired
OL,4,CMorrisons manager who confronted
OL,5,Cshoplifter
OL,7,FThe shoplifter has since been
OL,8,Fconvicted and sentenced in relation to
OL,9,Fthe incident.
OL,11,FIn a media statement, a Morrisons
OL,12,Fspokesperson said: "We have very clear
OL,13,Fguidance, procedures and controls in
OL,14,Fplace to protect our colleagues and
OL,15,Fcustomers from the risk of harm, which
OL,16,Fmust be strictly followed.
OL,26,@tD@TOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/5
