CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F346A1782778699
OL,3,CFundraiser passes #20000 for fired
OL,4,CMorrisons manager who confronted
OL,5,Cshoplifter
OL,7,F"These include detailed procedures for
OL,8,Fhandling shoplifting incidents, which
OL,9,Fare in place to protect both the
OL,10,Fcolleague involved and surrounding
OL,11,Fcolleagues and customers, and which
OL,12,Fseek to de-escalate and calmly control
OL,13,Fthe situation."
